{"tid":1303081,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今年補過yylam嘅同學仔入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T02:41:59.000Z","uid":137134,"like":100,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba012e8549624c6689d23b9e6b2409e2a541f91f","tid":1303081,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"今日放榜，小妹補yylam拎左lv2，覺得人生真係好美好。<br />\n<br />\n本來見到自己成績咁撚差，又浪費左老豆老母辛苦賺返黎嘅補習錢，真係好想喊。但係，突然猛然回想起欣師講過「係我眼中，你地全部都係5**!」我就已經出撚晒水，成個人精鳩神晒~!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯!人生5**就好，其他都係浮雲! 再加上欣師平時都有買珍珠奶茶畀我地飲，其實計返條數，補習嘅錢冇蝕到，3年高中加加埋埋都有好多杯珍珠奶茶，呢個lv2絕對值得攞!"},{"pid":"031c5f720b33f756bb8c1d9dc0f904015ebdba6c","tid":1303081,"uid":66044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"爛尾文呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583ece9c4fdb3348906b0d8cb6e4190f05700904","tid":1303081,"uid":137134,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:35:44.000Z","msg":"欣師真係我人生嘅導師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年補佢拎左lv2 順利入左i大 <br />\n一完i大夢 我係ig留言多謝佢幫我拎到lv2 <br />\n可能佢份人太謙虛 連我嘅comment都del埋 <br />\n仲block左我 欣師真係好謙虛 唔俾學生多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nKris lau 我都補過 佢都好謙虛 <br />\n補佢我拎左lv2 真係好多謝佢 <br />\n我係ig direct多謝佢 <br />\n佢竟然話我係侏儒打手 <br />\nKris lau真係用心良苦 又係唔俾學生多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上兩位係我人生導師 教識我謙遜低調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e5c84fbecc27d23c4b0ea58b492f2d0aac2e7b","tid":1303081,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031c5f720b33f756bb8c1d9dc0f904015ebdba6c","tid":1303081,"uid":66044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"爛尾文呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-